Asides
You can include notes or even plots “aside” (to the right) your article:




Here the funny fact or some important info.



Equations
You can use a Latex syntax for it:

$$\sigma = \sqrt{ \frac{1}{N} \sum_{i=1}^N (x_i -\mu)^2}$$

\[
